Alchemical transformations are a puzzle which the user has to navigate. It acts as a sort of maze which is traversable. Think of the maze as a graph. Facets are nodes in the graph and treatments (or mixtures?) are edges.


Treatments
- Sun/Moon exposure: move around a cycle of n facets.
- Calcination (anoxic too?)
- Acidic digestion (type of acid matters)
